### Test 1: Get non-existent product (404)
GET http://localhost:54955/api/products/999

### Expected Response:
# {
#     "status": 404,
#     "error": "Resource Not Found",
#     "message": "Product not found with id: '999'"
# }

### Test 2: Create duplicate product (409)
POST http://localhost:54955/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Duplicate Product",
    "sku": "LAP-001",
    "price": 99.99,
    "stockQuantity": 10,
    "category": "Electronics"
}

### Test 3: Invalid login (401)
POST http://localhost:54955/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "wrong@email.com",
    "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### Test 4: Access admin endpoint without admin role (403)
GET http://localhost:54955/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

### Test 5: Add to cart with insufficient stock (409)
POST http://localhost:54955/api/cart/add/1?quantity=999999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}